thread.title: Ros Chiu
thread.title_full: Ink Station reviewed by Ros Chiu

author: Ros Chiu
title: Ros Chiu
text: Inkstation is always reliable, delivered what they promised, ordered in the morning and goods delivered in the afternoon on the same day. Their return of goods and refund process is simple when the compatible ink I received one time all I need was just ring support and guided me through with no fuss. Keep up with the good work.
